This '''glossary of geography terms''' is a list of definitions of terms and concepts used in [[geography]] and related fields, which describe and identify natural [[phenomena]], [[Location (geography)|geographical locations]], spatial dimension and [[natural resources]]. Geographical terms are classified according to their functions, such as [[description]], [[explanation]], [[Analysis|analysing]], [[Evaluation|evaluating]] and integrating.

{{compact ToC
