<span id="remote sensing"></span>{{term|term='''[[remote sensing]]'''}}
{{defn|defn=The gathering of information about an object or place from a remote location (i.e. without making physical on-site observations), most commonly by the use of satellite- or aircraft-based electromagnetic sensor technologies.}}

<span id="reservoir"></span>{{term|term='''[[reservoir]]'''}}
{{ghat|Also called an '''impoundment'''.}}
{{defn|defn=An artificial {{gli|lake}} or an artificially enlarged natural lake that is used to store water. Reservoirs are often created by the construction of a [[dam]] or [[lock (water navigation)|lock]] in a natural {{gli|drainage basin}}.}}

<span id="resource"></span>{{term|term='''[[resource]]'''}}
