The continent of [[Africa]] is commonly divided into five [[region]]s or [[subregion]]s, four of which are in [[Sub-Saharan Africa]].

== List of subregions in Africa ==
The five UN subregions:

* '''[[North Africa|Northern Africa]]'''
* '''[[East Africa|Eastern Africa]]'''
* '''[[Central Africa]]'''
* '''[[West Africa|Western Africa]]'''
* '''[[Southern Africa]]'''

