'''Odranski Obrež''' is a village in [[Central Croatia]], located south of [[Zagreb]]. The population is 1,578 (census 2011).<ref name="census2011">{{Croatian Census 2011|S|21|accessdate=2013-09-06|title=City of Zagreb}}</ref>

